.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-BOLT12-DECODE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-bolt12-decode \- decode a BOLT12 offer or invoice
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-bolt12-decode
.I offer_string
.SH DESCRIPTION
Decodes a BOLT12 offer or invoice string using CLN's decode command.
.PP
Output: JSON object from CLN's decode command.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-bolt12-decode (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-decode (1)
